</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Unitech, the electronic components group, has sold Rathdown Industries, the
payphone manufacturer, for Pounds 10.8m. The buyer is GN Investments, a
subsidiary of Great Nordic, the Danish telecommunications company.
Mr Peter Curry, chairman of Unitech, said Rathdown did not fit into
