wells will be drilled later this year.
Ultramar's Australian interests, including the Katnook gas field, were sold
to Sagasco Resources for ADollars 8m (Pounds 3.4m).
Lasmo said it continues to explore for oil in Western Australia and in
particular on the north west shelf.
